OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772651487
OL,3,CMan arrested after attempted kidnap of
OL,4,Cwoman in Andover
OL,6,FPolice have arrested a man following
OL,7,Fan attempted kidnap in Andover.
OL,9,FOfficers from Hampshire Police were
OL,10,Fcalled at 5.32pm on Monday 2 March
OL,11,Fafter a woman in her 50s was hit by a
OL,12,Fwhite van, before being grabbed by the
OL,13,Fdriver and pulled towards the back of
OL,14,Fthe vehicle on Micheldever Road.
OL,16,FShe managed to fend off the man and
OL,17,Frun away. The woman phoned police and
OL,18,Fwas taken to hospital to receive
OL,19,Ftreatment for injuries to her knee,
OL,20,Fwrist and nose. She has since been
OL,21,Fdischarged from hospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
