FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772651487
OL,3,CMan arrested after attempted kidnap of
OL,4,Cwoman in Andover
OL,6,FPolice have described the suspect as a
OL,7,Fwhite male in his 20s or 30s, slim
OL,8,Fbuild, with dark hair, wearing a green
OL,9,Ffleece.
OL,11,FA 28-year-old man from Newquay has
OL,12,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of
OL,13,Fattempted kidnap and remains in
OL,14,Fcustody.
OL,16,FDetective Chief Inspector Dal Andrews,
OL,17,Ffrom Northern CID, said: "The woman
OL,18,Fand her family are being fully
OL,19,Fsupported by officers as we continue
OL,20,Four investigation into this incident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772651487
OL,3,CMan arrested after attempted kidnap of
OL,4,Cwoman in Andover
OL,6,F"I appreciate the understandable
OL,7,Fconcern that an incident such as this
OL,8,Fwill cause within the local community,
OL,9,Fbut I would like to reassure you that
OL,10,Fwe are doing everything we can to find
OL,11,Fout what has taken place.
OL,13,F"Local officers are in the area,
OL,14,Fcarrying out house-to-house enquiries
OL,15,Fand reviewing CCTV footage. To help
OL,16,Fwith our investigation, we would like
OL,17,Fto hear from anyone who saw what
OL,18,Fhappened and has not yet spoken to
OL,19,Fpolice. If you have any information,
OL,20,Fplease get in touch with us.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
