OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772651487
OL,3,CMan arrested after attempted kidnap of
OL,4,Cwoman in Andover
OL,6,F"We will also be carrying extra
OL,7,Fpatrols in the area, so please speak
OL,8,Fto a uniformed officer if you have any
OL,9,Ffurther information, concerns or
OL,10,Fquestions."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
